channel.title: I iped my friend.. how do i unban?
channel.description:
i have iped my friend testing.. i have done ::ipban (name)... then when it did it afterwards i did ::unban (name).. and he wasnt un-ip banned. if you know if there are any commands to unban him could you tell me.. also i would like to ad this from his player info folder and ask if any of this means anything with the bans:
[CHARACTER] character-height = 0 character-posx = 2098 character-posy = 4426 character-rights = 0 character-ismember = 0 character-messages = 0 character-lastconnection = 222-155-167-162.jetstream.xtra.co.nz character-lastlogin = 20090107 character-energy = 100 character-gametime = 0 character-gamecount = 3663
so if u know how to un-ip ban please tell me! thanks!

item.title: I iped my friend.. how do i unban?
item.dc:creator: @austyman austyman
item.description:
@austyman wrote:

go into your data file and look for banned ips and remove your friends!
hope that helped you!
